# Untracked *.pub files (e.g. local dev keys) are LOCAL ONLY by convention.
# This allowlist makes `git add -A` skip untracked .pub files — it does NOT
# protect already-tracked files. The SSOT for the committed trust roots is
# pinned by .github/workflows/trusted-keys-allowlist.yml.
#
# For local dev signing, drop *.pub files into
# $NEXUS_LOCAL_TRUSTED_KEYS_DIR (default convention: ~/.nexus/trusted_keys/)
# and start the daemon with that env var set — see loader.rs for the
# runtime-trust-dir contract.
*.pub
!nexus-team.pub
!kernel-dogfood-v1.pub
